<v-content>
  <v-form
    ref="login"
    @submit.prevent="onSubmit()"
  >
    <v-text-field
      required
      v-model="form.token"
      prepend-icon="business"
      name="token"
      label="One Time Token"
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
      required
      v-model="form.pin"
      prepend-icon="person"
      name="pin"
      label="Pin"
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-card-actions>
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
      <v-btn
        :loading="locked"
        type="submit"
        color="deep-purple"
        dark
      > Impersonate </v-btn>
    </v-card-actions>
  </v-form>
</v-content>
